msgid "Spiritual Seekers and Mystics"
msgstr "Raadiyeyaasha Ruuxeed iyo Sirta"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Curious, introspective, open-minded, and drawn to "
"esoteric knowledge. They may have a strong interest in uncovering hidden "
"meanings or patterns in life. Occupations: Spiritual coaches, tarot readers,"
" astrologers, or individuals involved in New Age practices. Ideological "
"Spectrum: Likely to lean toward spiritual or metaphysical beliefs. They may "
"see the tools as a way to connect with deeper truths or universal energies."
msgstr ""
"Astaamaha Shakhsiyadda: Xiiso leh, nafsiyan, maskax furan, oo ku dhowaada "
"aqoonta qarsoon. Waxay yeelan karaan xiiso xooggan oo ay ku ogaadaan macnaha"
" qarsoon ama qaababka nolosha. Shaqooyinka: Tababareyaal ruuxeed, "
"akhristayaal tarot, xiddig-sare, ama dad ku lug leh dhaqamada New Age. "
"Spectrumka Falsafada: Waxaa suurtogal ah inay ku qabsadaan rumaysiin ruuxeed"
" ama meta-fizik. Waxay u arki karaan qalabka hab loo xiriiriyo xaqiiqada "
"qoto dheer ama tamarta guud."

msgid "Numerologists and Gematria Enthusiasts"
msgstr "Numbaraqistayaasha iyo Jamaarista Gematria"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Analytical, detail-oriented, and fascinated by the "
"relationship between numbers and language. They may enjoy decoding symbolic "
"meanings. Occupations: Freelance numerologists, writers on esoteric topics, "
"or hobbyists exploring numerology. Ideological Spectrum: May range from "
"those who view numerology as a fun intellectual exercise to those who "
"believe in its profound spiritual significance."
msgstr ""
"Astaamaha Shakhsiyadda: Falanqeyn, diiradda saaraya faahfaahinta, oo xiiso u"
" leh xiriirka u dhexeeya tirooyinka iyo luqadda. Waxay ku raaxeysan karaan "
"inay furtaan macnaha astaanta. Shaqooyinka: Numbaraqistayaal xor ah, "
"qorayaal ku saabsan mowduucyada qarsoon, ama hobiisteyaasha baadhaya "
"numarolojiyada. Spectrumka Falsafada: Waxay ka socdaan kuwa u arka "
"numarolojiyada sidii jimicsi xiiso leh ilaa kuwa aaminsan muhiimada ruuxeed "
"ee qoto dheer."

msgid "Historians and Linguists"
msgstr "Taariikhyahano iyo Luqateyaal"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Scholarly, methodical, and interested in historical or "
"cultural contexts of numerical systems like Abjad. Occupations: Academics, "
"researchers, or students studying Middle Eastern languages, history, or "
"religious texts. Ideological Spectrum: Likely to approach the tools from a "
"secular, academic perspective, focusing on their historical or linguistic "
"significance."
msgstr ""
"Astaamaha Shakhsiyadda: Aqoon leh, nidaamsan, oo xiiseeya xaalada "
"taariikhiga ah ama dhaqanka ee nidaamyada tirooyinka sida Abjad. "
"Shaqooyinka: Aqoon-isweynaha, cilmi-baarayaal, ama ardayda ku barta luqadaha"
" Bariga Dhexe, taariikhda, ama qoraallada diimeed. Spectrumka Falsafada: "
"Waxaa suurtogal ah inay si madax-bannaan uga falanqeeyaan qalabka, diiradda "
"saaraya taariikhda ama luqadda."

msgid "Religious or Faith-Based Individuals"
msgstr "Qof diimeed ama aaminaad ku saleysan"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Devout, reflective, and seeking deeper connections to "
"their faith. They may use the tools to explore religious texts or divine "
"messages. Occupations: Religious scholars, imams, priests, or laypeople with"
" a strong interest in their faith’s mystical traditions. Ideological "
"Spectrum: Likely to have a traditional or conservative worldview, using the "
"tools to reinforce their spiritual beliefs."
msgstr ""
"Astaamaha Shakhsiyadda: Diimeed, ka fikiraya, oo raadinaya xiriir qoto dheer"
" oo ay la leeyihiin aaminaadda. Waxay u isticmaali karaan qalabka si ay u "
"baaraan qoraallada diimeed ama farriimaha Ilaaha. Shaqooyinka: Aqoon-"
"isweynaha diimeed, imama, kaniisada, ama dad aan xeer ka tirsanayn oo leh "
"xiiso xooggan oo ku saabsan dhaqanka sirta ee aaminaadda. Spectrumka "
"Falsafada: Waxaa suurtogal ah inay leeyihiin aragti dhaqameed ama xeer-"
"qabta, isticmaalaya qalabka si ay u xoojiso rumaysinnada ruuxiga ah."

msgid "Writers and Artists"
msgstr "Qorayaal iyo Fannaan"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Creative, imaginative, and drawn to symbolic or abstract"
" concepts. They may use the tools for inspiration or to add layers of "
"meaning to their work. Occupations: Authors, poets, visual artists, or "
"musicians. Ideological Spectrum: May range from secular creatives to those "
"with a spiritual or mystical bent."
msgstr ""
"Astaamaha Shakhsiyadda: Hal-abuur, fikir-aha, oo ku dhowaada fikradaha "
"astaan ama abstrak. Waxay u isticmaali karaan qalabka dhiirrigelin ama inay "
"ku darsadaan lakabyo macne leh shaqadooda. Shaqooyinka: Qoraa, gabay-sheeko,"
" fannaan muuqaal, ama muusig. Spectrumka Falsafada: Waxay ka socdaan hal-"
"abuur madax-bannaan ilaa kuwa leh aragti ruuxi ama sirta."

msgid "Puzzle and Riddle Enthusiasts"
msgstr "Hobistayaasha Xeerka iyo Su'aalaha"

msgid "Conspiracy Theorists and Alternative Thinkers"
msgstr "Fikirayaasha Qiyaasaha iyo Fikirayaasha Beddelka"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Skeptical of mainstream narratives, drawn to uncovering "
"hidden truths or patterns in systems. Occupations: Independent researchers, "
"bloggers, or activists. Ideological Spectrum: May have a more radical or "
"unconventional worldview, using the tools to support alternative theories or"
" narratives."
msgstr ""
"Astaamaha Shakhsiyadda: Sharad leh oo ku saabsan sheekooyinka caadiga ah, ku"
" dhowaada ogaanshaha xaqiiqo qarsoon ama qaababka nidaamyada. Shaqooyinka: "
"Cilmi-baarayaal madax-bannaan, bloggare, ama hawlgalayaasha. Spectrumka "
"Falsafada: Waxay yeelan karaan aragti xiiso badan ama aan caadi ahayn, "
"isticmaalaya qalabka si ay u taageeraan aragtiyada ama sheekooyinka kale."

